                        break="no" n="31"/>υπόδικοι. <w lemma="ἀγγράφω">ἀγγράψαι</w> δὲ καὶ τὸ <rs type="institution" subtype="object" role="decreeing" key="dogma" ref="#lato"><w lemma="δόγμα">δόγμα</w></rs> ἐς τὸ <rs type="institution" subtype="public_space" role="inscription_setup" key="hieron" ref="#lato"><w lemma="ἱερόν">ἱερὸν</w> τᾶς <persName type="divine" key="Eleuthyia">Ἐλευθυίας</persName></rs>.
